item.description: Linus Future coder and military enthusiast My name is Linus and I am 1/3 of team Game of Code. I have one goal in life and that is to always make the best of things. Since I love problemsolving and computers I decided to go into codeing since I tought I would like it wich I did, a lot. I just stated codeing with a one month full time course in Java this summer before I started this one year education.

About us About us We are Game of Code, we are coders. We are a small team constisting of 3 people who are getting educated in code. We have been workning with JAVA, C#, Html, Css, MySQL , Heroku, Netlify and Javascript. Right now our team is exploring the possibilities of GoHugo and that is the reason for this site. We are a positive team constantly searching for more knowledge in the coding area to become better at what we do.

Dexter Dexter Future coder and investor My name is Dexter and I am 1/3 of team Game of Code. I am a person who is positive about every aspect of life. There are many things I like to do, to see, and to experience. I like to play games, I like to gym, I like to learn new things, I like to hanging out with my friends and I do also like to listen to music.

Linnea Linnea Future coder and sleep-enthusiast. My name is Linnea and I am 1/3 of team Game of Code. My goal in life is to become a talanted coder whose good at solving problems. I have basic knowledge in some coding-languages, which you can find on the About us page if that interests you. I started to learn my first language at 17 years old which was html and css, and from there I went on to learn the basics in a few more and to use diffrent tools.
